text: Compsosoma fasciatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Monné in 1980. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma fasciatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1980
